<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3508] JS:TS Generator set all fields of the struct as required</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3508</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Generator omits all optional fields of struct by default set them to required.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s important don&apos;t make all fields of generated interface to be required.&lt;br/&gt;
For example I have a model that will be used in request as data and I want to send only required fields and in some cases additional optional fields in same request, but not all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Typescript interface with required fields must be fully filled, if some fields will be omit it will cause error. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks and please resolve that ASAP.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
